  schema={schema}
>
  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Best Gaming Monitors (2026)</h1>
      <p>We compared 12 gaming monitors across every resolution, panel type, and budget. Here are the ones actually worth buying.</p>
